(* Proof:
   By contradiction, assume (r <:> s) = 0.
   Since FiniteVSpace s r.sum $*         by finite_subfield_is_finite_vspace_scalar
      so r.sum.carrier = {r.sum.id}      by finite_vspace_dim_eq_0
      or             R = {#0}            by field_carriers
